	heroSubhead={`You run toward what everyone else runs from. You carry calls no one should have to carry, and you do it again the next shift. Here's the truth underneath the uniform: you have a Father in heaven who sees exactly what you've seen — and runs toward you the way you run toward everyone else.`}
	heroBase={`https://cdn.sanity.io/images/rusi1hyi/production/6b5222bc14effb6cedb9f1f7a87aeb73c39fc24e-1100x733.jpg`}
