	offersBlocks={[
		{ heading: `A refuge for the one who shelters everyone`, bodyHtml: `You're who people run to — but you have somewhere to run too. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/psalms/91" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Your Father is your refuge and fortress</a>, the shelter that holds you when the shift finally ends.` },
		{ heading: `Strength you don't have to fake`, bodyHtml: `You don't have to manufacture courage alone: <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/isaiah/41" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">your Father strengthens you and holds you up</a> — real strength for the next call, not a mask you keep adjusting.` },
		{ heading: `Rest for the weary`, bodyHtml: `After the worst shifts, <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/matthew/11" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">your Father invites the weary and burdened to come</a> — and His whole promise is rest for the soul you've worn thin.` },
		{ heading: `Nearness when your heart is broken`, bodyHtml: `The calls that crush you don't push Him away — <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/psalms/34" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">your Father is close to the brokenhearted</a> and stays near the crushed in spirit.` },
	]}
	whyHeading={`Why the Father's Heart Bible™ for first responders`}
	whyBlocks={[
		{ heading: `You meet God as a Father, not a chaplain's cliche`, bodyHtml: `You've heard the lines — "thoughts and prayers," "stay strong." The Father's Heart Bible™ is different: it reveals God as a <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture does — from <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Genesis 1</a> on. Not one more voice telling you to be tough, but the One who runs toward you and stays.` },
		{ heading: `It's free, on your phone, with audio for any shift`, bodyHtml: `No account, no purchase, no app. <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Read it free online</a> with audio on every chapter — listen in the rig, on a quiet stretch of patrol, or when the calls replay at 3 a.m. The Father's voice fits right into your real shift.` },
		{ heading: `It speaks to the trauma you actually carry`, bodyHtml: `Hypervigilant? Grieving a call? Wondering if anyone sees the cost? Start with our <a href="/verses/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">verses by topic</a> or learn to talk to Him with our <a href="/guides/how-to-pray/" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">how-to-pray guide</a> — the Word meets you right where the job leaves you.` },
